snippet.title: Qisah Tomang: Cycle Ends Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2227810/Qisah_Tomang_Cycle_Ends/

Qisah Tomang: Cycle Ends is a story-rich RPG. The story is set in an East Asia inspired fantasy world. Fight off the Demon Tomang and its minion and discover the truth behind the Cycle of Hatred and put an end to it in this classic pixel RPG.

Made with RPG Maker MV
Trailer made by https://www.youtube.com/@shikusukata_2441
